(20, 72, 19, 'Python', 'P1001', 'Python', '<p>Learn to Program and Analyze Data with Python. Develop programs to gather, clean, analyze, and visualize data.</p>', '<p><span style=\"color: #373a3c; font-family: \'Source Sans Pro\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff;\">This Specialization builds on the success of the Python for Everybody course and will introduce fundamental programming concepts including data structures, networked application program interfaces, and databases, using the Python programming language. In the Capstone Project, you&rsquo;ll use the technologies learned throughout the Specialization to design and create your own applications for data retrieval, processing, and visualization.</span></p>', '<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: #4f5052; font-family: \'segoe UI\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">What you&rsquo;ll learn</h5>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 18px; list-style: none; color: #4f5052; font-family: \'segoe UI\'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0rem 0px 2px; list-style: disc;\">Understand the Time Value of Money</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0rem 0px 2px; list-style: disc;\">Understand and Calculate the Net Present Value, Internal Rate of Return, and Payback Period for Capital Budgeting</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0rem 0px 2px; list-style: disc;\">Calculate the Future Value and Present Value of cash flows Theory?</li>\r\n</ul>', '<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: #4f5052; font-family: \'segoe UI\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">Requirements</h5>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: