(36, 68, 23, 'Agile with Atlassian Jira', 'AAJ0023', 'Agile-with-Atlassian-Jira', '<p><span style=\"color: #373a3c; font-family: OpenSans, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff;\">This course discusses common foundational principles and practices used by agile methodologies, providing you with a flexible set of tools to use in your role (e.g. product owner, scrum master, project manager, team member) on an agile team. Learn agile and lean principles</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: #373a3c; font-family: OpenSans, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff;\">This course discusses common foundational principles and practices used by agile methodologies, providing you with a flexible set of tools to use in your role (e.g. product owner, scrum master, project manager, team member) on an agile team. Learn agile and lean principles, including kanban and scrum, and use Jira Software Cloud as the tool to apply hands-on exercises in these topics. The course includes instruction on company-managed and team-managed Jira projects. </span></p>', '<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: #4f5052; font-family: \'segoe UI\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">What you&rsquo;ll learn</h5>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 18px; list-style: none; color: #4f5052; font-family: \'segoe UI\'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0rem 0px 2px; list-style: disc;\">Understand the Time Value of Money</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0rem 0px 2px; list-style: disc;\">Understand and Calculate the Net Present Value, Internal Rate of Return, and Payback Period for Capital Budgeting</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0rem 0px 2px; list-style: di