(59, 117, 29, 'Introduction to English Common Law', 'IECL0036', 'Introduction-to-English-Common-Law', '<p><span style=\"color: #373a3c; font-family: OpenSans, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff;\">This MOOC will give you an introduction to this influential legal system including its history, constitutional background, sources and institutions. You&rsquo;ll learn about the different ways in which laws are made and interpreted.</span></p>', '<p><span style=\"color: #373a3c; font-family: OpenSans, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #ffffff;\">This MOOC will give you an introduction to this influential legal system including its history, constitutional background, sources and institutions. You&rsquo;ll learn about the different ways in which laws are made and interpreted, the English court system and the increasing importance of European Union and human rights law. Now is an especially exciting time to be learning about English common law, given the potential changes that lie ahead in today&rsquo;s political, economic and social environment &ndash; all these pose challenges to and opportunities for the law.</span></p>', '<h5 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-weight: normal; line-height: 1.2; font-size: 24px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: #4f5052; font-family: \'segoe UI\'; background-color: #ffffff;\">What you&rsquo;ll learn</h5>\r\n<ul style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 18px; list-style: none; color: #4f5052; font-family: \'segoe UI\'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #ffffff;\">\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0rem 0px 2px; list-style: disc;\">Understand the Time Value of Money</li>\r\n<li style=\"box-sizing: border-box; padding: 0px; margin: 0rem 0px 2px; list-style: disc;\">Understand and Calculate the Net Present Value, Internal Rate of Return, and Payback Period for Capital Budgeting</li>\r\n<li 