(56, 52, 'Ritika', '', 'Arora', 'ritika-arora-52', '<p><span style=\"color: #374151; font-family: S&ouml;hne, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, \'Segoe UI\', Roboto, Ubuntu, Cantarell, \'Noto Sans\', sans-serif, \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: #f7f7f8;\">Hi, I am an Instructional Designer with a background in education. I want to dedicate my career to improving the way people learn. With an in-depth understanding of the field, I am passionate about designing engaging and effective learning experiences.</span></p>', 'base_56_1675766344Profile Thmubnail .jpg', '<p>Designing and developing&nbsp;<strong>e-learning</strong>&nbsp;on cross-cultural communication, time management techniques, and a certification programme in project management.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Classroom instruction and workshop facilitation</strong>&nbsp;- Running a full-day team-building workshop, a half-day course on active listening, and training on presentation techniques.</p>\r\n<p>Delivering&nbsp;<strong>virtual training (VILT)&nbsp;</strong>on conflict resolution, running a webinar on time management strategies, or teaching a live online course on negotiating skills.</p>\r\n<p>The development of&nbsp;<strong>micro-learning and gamification</strong>&nbsp;for brief interactive learning modules on customer service, the use of gamification to train staff about workplace safety and the creation of bite-sized lectures on product knowledge.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Performance support and job aids&nbsp;</strong>- Creating a quick reference guide for a piece of software, creating a work aid to assist staff in resolving technical issues, or establishing a mobile app that offers sales representatives in the field real-time performance support.</p>', 'profile_56_1675766344minimalistic W.jpg', 'award_56_1675766388Wallpaper.png', '2023-02-03 07:36:48'),
(57, 55, 'Dr Susan ', '', 'Davis', 'dr-susan-davis-55', '<p>I am Dr. Susan Davis, DNP, MSN, RN, PMD, and I am proud at this point in my career to be creating a digital space that reaches thousands and, hopefully, millions of nurses around the world with a message of courage, confidence, and excellence in the practice of life-saving resuscitation.</p>', 'base_57_16757504463.jpg', '<p>&nbsp;I have trained more than 50,000 American nurses and healthcare professionals in Basic, Advanced, and Pediatric resuscitation response and improved code blue team performance.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>I have learned a lot by listening to nurses I have trained and have worked beside in code blue situations;</p>\r\n<p>There is a better way to improve nurse-empowered resuscitation performance, and my program, CodePRep,&trade; offers quick and effective code blue training to individual nurses, healthcare, and long term care facilities. We encourage and empower bedside teams to respond at the top of their licensing and training.</p>', 'profile_57_16757504461.jpg', 'award_57_1675752006award_13_award_5_bannerProfile.jpg', '2023-02-07 06:03:39'),
