ent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin: 0px;\">Performance Support: Design and development of performance support tools, such as job aids and quick reference guides, to help learners apply their newly acquired knowledge and skills on the job.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"border: 0px solid #d9d9e3; box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0.375em;\">\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px solid #d9d9e3; box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin: 0px;\">Evaluation and Assessment: Evaluation of training programs to measure their impact and effectiveness, including formative and summative assessments.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n<li style=\"border: 0px solid #d9d9e3; box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin: 0px; padding-left: 0.375em;\">\r\n<p style=\"border: 0px solid #d9d9e3; box-sizing: border-box; --tw-border-spacing-x: 0; --tw-border-spacing-y: 0; --tw-translate-x: 0; --tw-translate-y: 0; --tw-rotate: 0; --tw-skew-x: 0; --tw-skew-y: 0; --tw-scale-x: 1; --tw-scale-y: 1; --tw-scroll-snap-strictness: proximity; --tw-ring-offset-width: 0px; --tw-ring-offset-color: #fff; --tw-ring-color: rgba(59,130,246,0.5); --tw-ring-offset-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-ring-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow: 0 0 transparent; --tw-shadow-colored: 0 0 transparent; margin: 0px;\">Learning Management Systems: Implementation and management of learning management systems to deliver, track, and manage training programs.</p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>', '<p>We specialise in assisting businesses with the creation and execution of efficient training and development initiatives. Typically, our consulting entails the following actions:</p>\r\n<p>Assessment: To find opportunities for improvement, the consultation team will evaluate the organization\'s present training and development initiatives. This can entail conducting staff interviews, focus groups, or surveys.</p>\r\n<p>The consultation team will provide recommendations for strengthening the organization\'s training and development programmes based on the assessment. This could involve ideas for revamping current curricula, creating brand-new curricula, or introducing fresh technology.</p>\r\n<p>Design and Development: The consultant team will collaborate with the business to create specialised training programmes that address its unique needs and objectives. This could involve developing lesson plans, teaching techniques, and evaluation procedures.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>', '', '', '2023-02-07 12:07:38'),
